@nolanbernard

False...movies have not been shot on film in years. Yes, there are several 35MM projectors out there (my old theatre was an arthouse and only converted a few to Digital), but the vast majority of theatres are converting to almost all Digitals, as it reduces film conversion and shipping costs.

Our IMAX projector is Digital as well. 35MM Projectors and 75MM IMAX Projectors are a thing of the past now..
